<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <link 
            rel="stylesheet" 
            href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
            integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" 
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        >
        <title>BugTrucker</title>
        <script>
            document.onreadystatechange = () => {
                if(document.readyState === 'interactive') {
                    document.getElementById('userAgent').value = window.navigator.userAgent
                    document.getElementById('userDate').value = new Date()
                }
            }
        </script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">BugTracker</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="container"> 
            <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                Seu problema foi reportado com sucesso. Muito obrigado.<a href="/">Voltar e reportar outro problema</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </body>
</html>